            <td width="550" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#e7e4e1" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:20px; color:#333333;">

This appeal was sent out to all parents and guardians, and we raised a phenomenal £16,000 through generous donations. It feels appropriate to thank each and every one of you who donated to this cause, ensuring that everyone who wants to do NCS with The Challenge, has the financial assistance to do so. Thank you very much for digging deep, particularly in today's economic climate.<BR><BR>

Our online appeal is still open - as we try to reach our target of £20,000. Therefore, if you did not have the opportunity to donate previously, and would like to so - please <a href="https://mydonate.bt.com/events/tcnbursaries">click here</a>.<BR><BR>

A sincere thank you to you all, and the very best wishes for the festive period.


            <BR><BR>
 

            <strong>Yours sincerely,</strong><br />
            <img src="http://www.the-challenge.org/email-newsletters/parents-salesforce-template-2012/tcn-craig-morley-020712.jpg" alt="Craig Morley" width="216" height="57" border="0" /><br />
